articles.title: MasterChef Australia judge Jock Zonfrillo secretly battled bowel cancer, says report - Times of India
articles.description: MasterChef Australia judge Jock Zonfrillo secretly battled cancer before passing away on April 30. The 46 year old was found dead in a hotel room in Melbourne around 2 am. ​
